data.description: LOCATION. LOCATION. LOCATION. Introducing an exceptional find! Spacious and inviting condo that checks all the boxes! This stunning residence features 2 BR, 2 full baths, and 2 .5 bath.   Well-appointed kitchen. Upgraded cabinets, SS appliances, and granite hard surfaces create a modern and stylish space. Kitchen opens to a cathedral great room with luxury upgraded flooring throughout. One of the highlights of this condo is the 1st floor primary en suite, offering convenience and privacy. The lower level offers a finish living space w/ fireplace and 1/2 bath. Newer deck 2022, newer water heater 2023.
